  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are some ways to restore a Compaq computer to factory settings?",
  "response": "Restoring a Compaq computer to its factory settings can help resolve various issues and improve performance. Here are some ways to perform a factory reset on a Compaq computer:\n\n1. **Using Recovery Partition**:\n   - **Step 1**: Turn off the computer.\n   - **Step 2**: Turn on the computer and immediately press the `F11` key repeatedly until the Recovery Manager screen appears.\n   - **Step 3**: Select \"System Recovery\" and follow the on-screen instructions to restore the computer to factory settings.\n\n2. **Using Recovery Discs**:\n   - **Step 1**: If you have recovery discs, insert the first disc into the CD/DVD drive.\n   - **Step 2**: Restart the computer.\n   - **Step 3**: When prompted, press any key to boot from the CD/DVD.\n   - **Step 4**: Follow the on-screen instructions to restore the computer using the recovery discs.\n\n3. **Using Windows Settings (Windows 8/10/11)**:\n   - **Step 1**: Open the `Settings` app (you can do this by pressing `Windows key + I`).\n   - **Step 2**: Navigate to `Update & Security`.\n   - **Step 3**: Select `Recovery` from the left-hand menu.\n   - **Step 4**: Under \"Reset this PC,\" click `Get started`.\n   - **Step 5**: Choose `Remove everything` to perform a full factory reset, which will remove all your files and applications.\n   - **Step 6**: Follow the on-screen instructions to complete the process.\n\n4. **Using Boot Menu**:\n   - **Step 1**: Restart the computer.\n   - **Step 2**: Immediately press the `Esc` key repeatedly to access the startup menu.\n   - **Step 3**: Select `F11` for System Recovery.\n   - **Step 4**: Follow the on-screen instructions to restore the computer to factory settings.\n\n5. **Using Safe Mode**:\n   - **Step 1**: Restart the computer.\n   - **Step 2**: Press `F8` repeatedly as the computer is starting up to access Advanced Boot Options.\n   - **Step 3**: Select `Repair Your Computer`.\n   - **Step 4**: Choose your keyboard layout and login.\n   - **Step 5**: Select `Compaq Recovery Manager` and follow the on-screen instructions to perform the factory reset.\n\nBefore performing a factory reset, make sure to back up any important files, as this process will erase all personal data from the computer.",
